data.description: Impressive hill top home with beautiful panoramic views of the sunsets and private pond. This property offers 16.49+/-acres of unrestricted property, partially cleared and wooded. The home features 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, and open concept floor plan with living open to kitchen and dining. RV hookups on site, with large metal shop. This home and property has it all.
